metadata.name: Calladita Tier 1 – Still #1166
metadata.description:
CALLADITA is the genesis NFT collection by filmmaker Miguel Faus. It comprises 2.400 NFTs organized in 4 Tiers. All of the proceeds from these NFT sales will go towards funding Miguel’s first feature-length film, CALLADITA.
All utilities and full T&Cs can be found on the project’s website.
